# .sanitisation-patterns - extended-regex, one forbidden identifier per line.
# Blank lines and # comments are ignored. The gate fails the build if any of
# these appears in a tracked file. Adapt to YOUR invariants.
#
# Examples (replace with your own):
yourdomain\.example
\bYourHostnameA\b
\bYourHostnameB\b
10\.0\.0\.[0-9]+
\byour-username\b
